title: Vincent Van Gogh Art Print Portfolio
description:
This Art Portfolio contains 8 high-quality art reproductions printed on 200 gsm watercolor paper or satin-coated art paper. These papers are non-aging and manufactured from chlorine-free pulp by FSC and PEFC certified mills. The prints are enclosed in hardback portfolio covers made of premium paperboard with inner endpapers along with flaps for further protection. The portfolios have a high-quality cloth spine (made of rayon, a plant-based fiber) and a cotton ribbon closure.

  • 8 Print Reproductions
  • Dimensions: Portfolio 12.5 x 17.75 in, Prints 12 x 16.5 in.
  • Materials: 200 gsm watercolor paper or satin-coated art paper
